stories.title: Harbhajan makes his mark as India eclipse South Africa by 41 runs
stories.summary:
Harbhajan Singh introduced himself to South Africa in the most emphatic
manner at Supersport Park on Wednesday night, ripping the heart out of
the home team's batting to set up a 41-victory for India in the third
game of the Standard Bank One-Day
